descriptionHtml:

[size=4][b]Manual Installation :[/b]
[/size]
1. Download the Preset
2. Extract the file to a place of your choosing
3. Put the file in Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/Chargen/Presets
4. Once in the game, start a new game or type in "showracemenu"
5. Set race to "[i]Nord"[/i]Â and make sure you are on female
6. Then go to the Preset tab next to the tab that says sliders, and hit F9 and look for my preset
7. Click it, it should load, and there you go





[size=4][b]CREDITS :

[/b][/size]Bethesda For the game
and For all authors of the mods that is listed above
[/center]
